                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Skip forward a little bit by pressing once. completely skip through by pressing twice:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMEPLAY CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X or Triangle Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Attack via wind bullet / grab and throw enemies:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square or Circle Buttons</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Double jump:
